{"type": "article", "id": 27400, "title": "有山水的边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-27T06:53:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134113oIx6ju8KPeGFv7Ut.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p>\n<p>Peca 工作室的 Caterina Moretti 设计的这款边桌 <a href=\"http://www.peca.com.mx/#/isla/\">Isla</a> 看上去就像是在一面平静的湖水中升起了一座小岛。边桌取材自实心橡木、黄铜、石灰石和大理石，在 Moretti 的精心设计下，这四种对比鲜明的材质融合在了一起，仿佛还原了一幅山水画。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kichink.com/buy/825371\">购买链接</a>，售价为 911.68 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134111LFcbihypDUvxsw6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134111CNxc90AdVaYJk8r1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021341114fMU6krWPCd8zcHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134112bfLyoPYgCn2tZiST.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure>\n</div>"}